node.text:
I’m soo fucking proud of you brodie!!! I don’t have the words to express how proud I am of your MINDSET!! You have always inspired me, but now more than ever your will be my inspiration!! Your Resiliency and your will not to give up and give in has been amazing, and you should be proud. My lil bro is 30!!! And looking and feeling the best yet!! Keep going Brodie and keep inspiring others around you. I love you and HAPPY 30th Birthday!!🎂🎂🎂 

*we gonna celebrate when I get home 🤷🏾‍♂️lol 

#whynot

node.text:
I can’t even begin to put into words all of the emotions I have right now. It’s been one heck of a journey Oklahoma! When I came here, I was 18 years old, bright eyed, and completely unaware of all the amazing things that would soon take place. I grew up in Oklahoma with an amazing bunch of people. The people here are what makes this place so special. From the fans, my coaches, my teammates, the entire Thunder organization, Mr. Bennett, Sam Presti, my friends, and everyone in the entire community. You are all what makes Oklahoma such a beautiful place, and the reason I’ve loved playing here all of this time. You have supported me through all of the ups and the downs, and stood by me through the good times, and tough times. For that I am eternally grateful to you. I’ve met so many amazing people who have helped shape me into the man that I am today. I hope I have impacted the Oklahoma community as much as Oklahoma has made an impact on me and my family. 
I’m leaving Oklahoma with so many friends and so much gratitude. I could never thank you all enough for sticking with me. It’s been a dream and a whirlwind. #WHYNOT

#WhyNot?, a short film showcasing the culture of Los Angeles’ Crenshaw district which aims to expose youth to the ever-growing technology space. 

Coming 6.24 to the Jordan Community Page

#whynot

node.text: I stand for the community, always.  It was an honor to help re-open the @crenshawymca this week with family, friends, community leaders & young kids who will take part in a very special #WhyNot Academy program this summer.  Blessed to use my platform to empower & change lives for generations to come.  Big thanks to @jumpman23 @whynotfoundation @mrflowerfantastic!

node.text: Happy Father’s Day LovvveOnee! You have always showed me the way and I’m grateful to have you in my life every step of the way. Thank you for each and every life lesson, my role model always. Enjoy your day OG!! Love you Dad!

node.text: Dream beyond expectations #whynot. Last night we celebrated the world premiere of the short film WHY NOT? which is inspired by a mentality that I have honored in every aspect of my life. Very proud of the cast & crew for telling a story about finding your purpose and owning it. This is just the beginning!
